                                <div style="text-align: left;" class="mk-text-block  true">
                                    <p>Everyone has favorite pieces of jewelry – your wedding bands, that bracelet you wear every day, a necklace with special significance. Constant wear on jewelry, though, can create some issues. Maybe a stone has fallen out, perhaps your band is wearing thin or your necklace clasp is no longer working. These issues are easily solved in our jewelry repair department.</p>
                                    <p>DC of WNY offers full-service jewelry repair in-house. Rest assured that your jewelry will not leave the building and will be handled with the utmost care.</p>
                                    <p>It is also important to remember that jewelry looks its best when sparkling clean. Too many people wear jewelry every day without thinking about cleaning it. Bring your jewelry in to us where it can be cleaned by a professional. You’ll be amazed at the difference. Your diamonds will sparkle again, your gold will shine.</p>
